com.picocontainer.behaviors

Class AbstractBehavior.AbstractChangedBehavior<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.picocontainer.behaviors.AbstractBehavior.AbstractChangedBehavior<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ChangedBehavior<T>, ComponentAdapter<T>, ComponentLifecycle<T>, ComponentMonitorStrategy, LifecycleStrategy, Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AnnotatedStaticInjection.StaticInjection, Automating.Automated, Decorating.Decorated, FieldDecorating.FieldDecorated, Guarding.Guarded, ImplementationHiding.HiddenImplementation, Locking.Locked, PropertyApplying.PropertyApplicator, Storing.Stored, Synchronizing.Synchronized
    Enclosing class:
    AbstractBehavior

    public abstract static class AbstractBehavior.AbstractChangedBehavior<T>
extends Object
implements ChangedBehavior<T>, ComponentMonitorStrategy, LifecycleStrategy, Serializable

    Component adapter which decorates another adapter.

    This adapter supports a component monitor strategy and will propagate change of monitor to the delegate if the delegate itself support the monitor strategy.

    This adapter also supports a lifecycle manager and a lifecycle strategy if the delegate does.

    Author:
    Jon Tirsen, Aslak Hellesoy, Mauro Talevi
